                                     + ". It is not defined.", Project.MSG_WARN);
                  } catch (Throwable t) {
                      attributes.log("Unable to verify class " + classname
                                     + ". Loading caused Exception: "
                                     + t.getMessage(), Project.MSG_WARN);
                  }
              }
              return target;
          }
      }
